                </p>
                <ul class="achievements-list">
                    <li>Graduated as one of the top students in the class</li>
                    <li>Received recognition for academic excellence and good conduct</li>
                    <li>Participated in school sports and cultural activities</li>
                    <li>Demonstrated early aptitude for mathematics and logical reasoning</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-section">
            <h2>Certifications</h2>
            <div class="certifications-grid">
